    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add<strong> half </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> of the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>,<strong> Henderson’s Relish</strong>, a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong> and 225ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan and give everything a good stir</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining wholegrain mustard for another recipe!</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, then reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
